snippet.title: VOCES8
snippet.description:
The VOCES8 Foundation works to inspire people through music and is one of the leading vocal music education charities in the world. It is responsible for hundreds of professional concerts each year around the world by VOCES8 and Apollo5, a series of chart topping classical albums on Decca, Signum and VOCES8 Records, and sheet music and education resources published by Edition Peters. It runs an innovative and wide reaching education programme reaching 40,000 young people every year. 

This channel contains performance videos and online teaching resources by VOCES8, Apollo5 and Paul Smith. For more information, visit www.voces8.com - www.apollo5.co.uk - www.psv8.co.uk - www.voces8.foundation

Social media: @VOCES8 @TheApollo5 @hatchmyideas @voces8foundation

Many of the videos on this channel were filmed at the VOCES8 Centre, the home of the VOCES8 Foundation in the heart of the City of London.
